Kaasvola (roughly translated from [[Goblin]] as "hand word") is a [[sign language]] used throughout [[Darguun]], [[Droaam]], and the [[Shadow Marches]]. The language evolved from a similar visual-gestural [[language]] used by the [[Dhakaan]]i [[dar|goblinoid]] thousands of years ago.